" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"真係咁撚戇鳩就抵佢死啦<br />\nkeep住有post點會無人經營<br />\n唔識中文都識睇timestamp啦<br />\n<br />\n我就覺得條友唔係買account 純粹偷"},{"pid":"abe91bcdef9f62328eb4335b34b7a167e6cd7347","tid":2328930,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:35:52.000Z","msg":"Noted. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d105292cbccff3d7f089791d20e77719b14b5a3b","tid":2328930,"uid":64856,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:37:04.000Z","msg":"謝曬皮有喺ig story講俾人偷晒成個acct，信用卡被盜用碌咗一萬蚊，宜家轉咗去MeWe"},{"pid":"0c336200a1e169eff3499eecbaa1270cb479db07","tid":2328930,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"佢開咗MeWe講，但可能唔會長用<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/謝曬皮\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2F%E8%AC%9D%E6%9B%AC%E7%9A%AE&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=03e8a1e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/謝曬皮</a>"},{"pid":"14e4d3a2a9cc7ea7ee8e5166f55f3d38f079b82e","tid":2328930,"uid":203889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4a59b94ac851793af05881ceddd90d3a8cd326ce","tid":2328930,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"如果條友講嘅野係真<br />\n個買家真係有比錢買佢都係受害者喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T04:33:20.000Z","msg":"估係扮受害者"},{"pid":"3a4dceb54b506aa060be62f34f1dbfca3168f148","tid":2328930,"uid":44854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a59b94ac851793af05881ceddd90d3a8cd326ce","tid":2328930,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"如果條友講嘅野係真<br />\n個買家真係有比錢買佢都係受害者喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"好心比番人啦"},{"pid":"3e5691b0a6e79e125fa2a1f45143e5bd2038dc9f","tid":2328930,"uid":169648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:38:28.000Z","msg":"見到有人報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/StartChing/posts/200977148311307|\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FStartChing%2Fposts%2F200977148311307%7C&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=e01a7758\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/StartChing/posts/200977148311307|</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2YUNOi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2YUNOi.jpg&h=e9846f38&s={SIZE}\" /> 【#StartChingNews】<br />\n「謝曬皮」FB帳號被盗兼轉手，買家貼狗相求粉絲留低<br />\n世事無奇不有，大家有否想過一覺醒來，一個經營多年的Facebook粉絲專頁可以再也登入不了，更可怕的是專頁被極速「轉手」，賊人更涉嫌透過Facebook page盗用信用卡，以約一萬元購物，本土KOL兼畫家「謝曬皮」正是今次事件的主角，其粉絲專頁在 3日前被盗，專頁有逾15萬人追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n其後，謝曬皮於MeWe 及 IG story 指自己 Facebook專頁被盗，然而奇怪的是，今日下午約2時，有買家在謝曬皮專頁現身，貼上一張樣子可憐的小狗照片，指自己向他人購買粉絲專頁時，不知道專頁是偷來的，更聲稱對方向他說「這是他們的專頁，他們沒有時間繼續管理。」令他以為是管理員自願出售專頁，他自己也是被騙的受害者，最後更請求謝曬皮的專頁粉絲留下來，繼續支持他，全文如下：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hsDxztC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhsDxztC.jpg&h=71b64832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民怒插：「還page咪得囉。扮咩死狗呢？ 知道係不法途徑取得嘅仲瀨死？ 」大批粉絲也留言批評發文者，其後，畫家朋友「阿塗」指謝曬皮正處理事件，呼籲大家暫時不要取消讚好FB專頁，但可以到Instagram及 Mewe追蹤以示支持。<br />\n目前謝曬皮Facebook專頁已「死Link」，畫面上顯示：「此連結可能損壞，或是該網頁已被移除。請確認你要打開的連結是否正確。」<br />\n<br />\nStartChing記者正向謝曬皮了解事件，暫未獲回覆。"},{"pid":"dfb13e59fa4f136776e82cb7f31515a79a476806","tid":2328930,"uid":169648,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"揾到個網台因為呢件事專訪咗 謝曬皮<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3lOFjWVzkf4&amp;ab_channel=PassionTimeshk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3lOFjWVzkf4%26ab_c